 "remarks": "A tree -lined driveway leads you to the piece of paradise you&apos;ve been waiting for... Tucked away on a private acre at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac this beautifully maintained Ranch features an open concept with sunken living room, adjoining dining room, well-proportioned kitchen with breakfast nook, granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. Just off the kitchen is a family room with a fireplace. A sunlit media room adjacent to a bedroom and full bath has the potential to be a guest or in-law suite. The main level also includes a primary bedroom with a full bath, walk-in closet, skylights, plus two additional bedrooms, full bath, laundry room and an office or a possible 5th bedroom. The finished lower level adds flexible living space with a mudroom, game room, full bath, and a quartz countertop with a sink and refrigerator-ideal for entertaining. Enjoy a large deck overlooking an in-ground pool, gazebo and mature landscaping. Has city water, an oversized 2 car garage and much more! Sellers are requesting highest and best offers due by 5pm on 6/16",
